	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />TOP brand (and most other cheap Chinese programmers) have very limited programming support for PLDs; generally you're stuck with Lattice GALs and compatibles. It's really necessary to track down archaic programmers for their PLD programming algorithms if you're interested in programming PAL, more common GALs, PALCE or PEEL (and of course other types of SPLD and EPLD.)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


